><font color=#fcfefd>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000080><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/uverano.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Verano </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Soldier of the Federation</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#70DB93>(8/17/02 1:50:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> vox/naggy</span><hr size=1> Vox and naggy I would like to see us kill these two more often, then main problem with these raids is that they mostly have to be pick up because not enough people stay at the proper lvl for the raids, I personally wanna kill them both and I won't be going past lvl 52 until I do, so if some one who has actually killed Vox or Naggy could lead a raid so I can go past lvl 52 that would be great <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000060><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ustoneglacier.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Stoneglacier</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mob Acquisition Coordinator</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#70DB93>(8/17/02 5:07:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: vox/naggy</span><hr size=1> Go past 52 and just go on a HoT raid.  Its the same thing with less chaos.<br>I went on one naggy raid and I said I'd never do another.  It took waaaaaay too long, twice as long if you fail. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87219>Reign Cloud</a> <BR>56 Master of the Legion of Other Folk <BR>Stoneglacier Thanos <BR>52 Cleric ofLegion of Little Folk <BR>"The streets will flow with the blood of the nonbelievers!!!!" <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000080><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/bfederationofpovar.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=lotis>Lotis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Soldier of the Federation</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#70DB93>(8/17/02 8:36:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> You don't understand</span><hr size=1> Killing Vox/Naggy is a rite of passage or at least it is for some folks. I was able to accomplish Naggy this week on a pick up raid, while it did take quite awhile and some folks ninjaed 3 of the 8 drops... I did it, thats all that matters. Unfortunatly, the 2 Vox raid's I've done so far were total failures, accredited mostly to bad turn out and poor commitment. I would really love if Fed at least hosted a successful Vox raid, hell, I would even be open to another Naggy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000060><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ucloudsoul.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cloudsoul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>General of the Federation</span><br>  Posts: 309<br> <font color=#70DB93>(8/18/02 12:25:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: You don't understand</span><hr size=1> <br>Vox is more of a challenge and we did do it about 4months ago I think, suppose enough time has lapsed for us to have another go <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Besides with POM coming up I wouldn't mind having an extra stick.<br><br><br>Eldark<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000080><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Montegue</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#70DB93>(8/19/02 4:53:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> I love kiling those dwagons</span><hr size=1> Just before I moved I got to go with some EXCELLENT raiders on an open Naggy raid, and the next day we did Vox. I managed to win the Vox belt on the second raid. It is VERY much a rite of passage. <br><br>As an aside, there was some ettiqutte about Dragon/God loot I didnt know about, and was sternly reminded about by that raid leader, so it was a good learning experience for me. <br><br>BTW if Cheeba is out there, /sal you were absolutely right. Took some time listening to the folks at the Rangers Glade but I get where you were coming from. Humblest apologies for my reactions.<br><br>See y'all in game.<br><br>Montegue Lonerunner<br>53rd Season Ranger<br>Mystic Defiance<br><br>Monte <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000060><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub70.ezboard.com/uravilicuslolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravilicus LoLF</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Soldier of the Federation</span><br>  Posts: 84<br> <font color=#70DB93>(8/19/02 7:02:52 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I love kiling those dwagons</span><hr size=1> Anyone that goes to a Lady Vox / Lord Nagafen raid without a few hours to blow is likely setting themselves up for disappointment.  These raids can be a blast, but they can also be seriously frustrating.  The chances of winning loot is very, very small at best, and the chances for failure can be pretty high depending on the raid party make-up and experience.<br><br>Regardless, EVERYONE should attend at least one of each Vs Vox and Naggy.  I have been to several dragon raids with Ravilicus, and recently a few with Thunderbumm.  I have never won anything but the experiences have been some of the more interesting if for no other reason than fighting a dragon kicks ass.<br><br>These days with Aegolism, C3, Circle Buffs, Elemental blankets, melee twink weapon upgrades and whatnot these raids are really much easier!  The Fed should definately host a raid sometime soon, especially if we can get some high level support for clearing giants, etc.  A Cleric with a click stick can often turn the tide in a battle with combat resses, too. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=126.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showNextMessage?topicID=126.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.emailToFriend?topicID=126.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.threadControl?topicID=126.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/ffederationofpovarfrm3.subscribeUnregist